Enter the grim darkness of the future  where  there
is only war, in the Gold Edition of  the  acclaimed
real-time strategy  PC  game  franchise,  Warhammer
40,000: Dawn of War II. Including both the original
game, Dawn of War II, and the standalone  expansion
Dawn of War: Chaos Rising, the Dawn of War II  Gold
Edition challenges players to use the Space Marines
to defend humanity from a variety of ravenous alien
factions, as well as  the  traitorous  Chaos  Space
Marines.  The  Gold  Edition  contains  two  single
player  campaigns,  five  factions  to  command  in
online multiplayer, a co-op  gameplay  options  and
more.

The Gold Edition includes:

* Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War II
* Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War II - Chaos Rising
